## 6. Bulk User Creation Script

Reads usernames from a file and creates users.

```bash
#!/bin/bash

FILE="users.txt"

for user in $(cat $FILE); do
  useradd $user
  echo "User $user created."
done
```

💡 Shows: loops, file input, system admin basics.

